column5: Going to be fishing Lake of The Woods out of this camp next week. Can anyone give me any hotspots our tips for this area. Thanks.

Bus, I am familiar with the area, will be at Young's last week in Sep. Send me an email at [email protected] and let me know what you are interested in fishing for, your familiarity with the area, etc, and I'll try to help you. Bill Krejca
